{"prompt": "Generate a website for a restaurant chain. The website should be minimalist and use blue as the brand color.", "code": "<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"en\">\n<head>\n    <meta charset=\"UTF-8\">\n    <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\">\n    <title>Delicious Bites</title>\n    <style>\n        :root {\n            --primary-color: #2c3e50; /* Dark Blue */\n            --secondary-color: #34495e; /* Slightly lighter Blue */\n            --text-color: #ecf0f1; /* Light Gray */\n            --background-color: #1a252f; /* Very Dark Blue */\n            --accent-color: #1abc9c; /* Teal, as a subtle accent */\n        }\n\n        body {\n            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;\n            margin: 0;\n            padding: 0;\n            background-color: var(--background-color);\n            color: var(--text-color);\n            display: flex;\n            flex-direction: column;\n            min-height: 100vh;\n            overflow-x: hidden;\n        }\n\n        header {\n            background-color: var(--primary-color);\n            padding: 20px 40px;\n            text-align: center;\n            box-shadow: 0 2px 5px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3);\n            position: sticky;\n            top: 0;\n            z-index: 1000;\n        }\n\n        header h1 {\n            margin: 0;\n            font-size: 2.5em;\n            color: var(--text-color);\n        }\n\n        nav {\n            margin-top: 15px;\n        }\n\n        nav a {\n            color: var(--text-color);\n            text-decoration: none;\n            margin: 0 20px;\n            font-size: 1.1em;\n            transition: color 0.3s ease;\n        }\n\n        nav a:hover {\n            color: var(--accent-color);\n        }\n\n        .container {\n            max-width: 1000px;\n            margin: 50px auto;\n            padding: 30px;\n            background-color: var(--secondary-color);\n            border-radius: 8px;\n            box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4);\n            text-align: center;\n        }\n\n        h2 {\n            color: var(--accent-color);\n            font-size: 2em;\n            margin-bottom: 30px;\n        }\n\n        .menu-item, .location-info, .contact-info {\n            margin-bottom: 30px;\n            padding: 20px;\n            background-color: var(--background-color);\n            border-radius: 5px;\n            border-left: 5px solid var(--accent-color);\n        }\n\n        .menu-item h3, .location-info h3, .contact-info h3 {\n            margin-top: 0;\n            color: var(--text-color);\n            font-size: 1.5em;\n        }\n\n        .menu-item p {\n            font-size: 1.1em;\n            line-height: 1.6;\n        }\n\n        .menu-item .price {\n            color: var(--accent-color);\n            font-weight: bold;\n            font-size: 1.2em;\n        }\n\n        .location-list li, .contact-list li {\n            list-style: none;\n            margin-bottom: 15px;\n            font-size: 1.1em;\n        }\n\n        .location-list li span, .contact-list li span {\n            color: var(--accent-color);\n            font-weight: bold;\n            display: inline-block;\n            width: 100px;\n        }\n\n        footer {\n            background-color: var(--primary-color);\n            color: var(--text-color);\n            text-align: center;\n            padding: 20px 0;\n            margin-top: auto;\n            font-size: 0.9em;\n            box-shadow: 0 -2px 5px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3);\n        }\n\n        .signature {\n            color: var(--accent-color);\n        }\n    </style>\n</head>\n<body>\n    <header>\n        <h1>Delicious Bites</h1>\n        <nav>\n            <a href=\"#menu\">Menu</a>\n            <a href=\"#locations\">Locations</a>\n            <a href=\"#contact\">Contact</a>\n        </nav>\n    </header>\n\n    <div class=\"container\">\n        <section id=\"about\">\n            <h2>Taste the Difference</h2>\n            <p style=\"font-size: 1.2em; line-height: 1.7;\">\n                Welcome to Delicious Bites, where culinary passion meets fresh, high-quality ingredients. We offer a modern dining experience with a focus on delicious and satisfying meals.\n            </p>\n        </section>\n\n        <section id=\"menu\">\n            <h2>Our Signature Menu</h2>\n            <div class=\"menu-item\">\n                <h3>Gourmet Burger</h3>\n                <p>Juicy, flame-grilled patty with artisanal cheese, crisp lettuce, and our secret sauce on a toasted brioche bun.</p>\n                <p class=\"price\">$14.99</p>\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"menu-item\">\n                <h3>Salmon Delight</h3>\n                <p>Pan-seared salmon fillet served with roasted asparagus and a lemon-dill sauce.</p>\n                <p class=\"price\">$18.99</p>\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"menu-item\">\n                <h3>Veggie Power Bowl</h3>\n                <p>Quinoa base topped with roasted sweet potatoes, black beans, avocado, and a cilantro-lime dressing.</p>\n                <p class=\"price\">$12.99</p>\n            </div>\n        </section>\n\n        <section id=\"locations\">\n            <h2>Find Us</h2>\n            <div class=\"location-info\">\n                <h3>Downtown</h3>\n                <ul class=\"location-list\">\n                    <li><span>Address:</span> 123 Blue Street</li>\n                    <li><span>Hours:</span> Mon-Sun: 11 AM - 10 PM</li>\n                </ul>\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"location-info\">\n                <h3>Uptown</h3>\n                <ul class=\"location-list\">\n                    <li><span>Address:</span> 456 Avenue Cobalt</li>\n                    <li><span>Hours:</span> Mon-Sat: 11 AM - 9 PM</li>\n                    <li><span>Hours:</span> Sunday: Closed</li>\n                </ul>\n            </div>\n        </section>\n\n        <section id=\"contact\">\n            <h2>Get In Touch</h2>\n            <div class=\"contact-info\">\n                <ul class=\"contact-list\">\n                    <li><span>Phone:</span> 555-DELICIOUS</li>\n                    <li><span>Email:</span> info@deliciousbites.com</li>\n                    <li><span>Follow Us:</span> @DeliciousBites</li>\n                </ul>\n            </div>\n        </section>\n    </div>\n\n    <footer>\n        <p>&copy; 2023 Delicious Bites. All rights reserved.</p>\n        <p>Designed with <span class=\"signature\">passion</span>.</p>\n    </footer>\n</body>\n</html>"}